                        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$b">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                                 <p>This collection includes writings by Royal Dixon as well as other authors close to Dixon, biographical material, materials related to his teaching and his leadership of organizational activity, correspondence, research notes from his writings, and newspaper clippings the author collected. The collection is arranged to the folder level preserving the original arrangement as much as possible.</p>
